certain other people have been accepting it as gospel for some time 
if that is so perhaps it would explain why sylvia plaths 
grave has been so repeatedly vandalized ms parnaby and 
wingfields wording of their mischievous falsehood can be read to 
my mind very like an incitement for other misguided enthusiasts to 
desecrate the grave afresh 
